message.body: Is Katch free tomorrow? You should ask her to come out and play tomorrow too!
Haha that's random. You want to hang with Katch? She actually just texted me so that's a coincidence

It is. I can see. I don't know when she wants to go out
Tell her to come out and play!
I wound up asking Katch. She would've liked to come out with us actually. She has a shoot though this afternoon
I just called to say I'm shutting my phone off for the lecture so it doesn't ring.
